## Summary
This Japanese documentation explains how to create personalized recommendations in Amplitude Activation, covering the step-by-step process of defining outcome events, building item catalogs from exposure events and event properties, configuring holdout groups for control measurement, and interpreting confidence scores and recommendation results.

